Phase 6 → Signal & Frame  
Phase 7 → Explain & Educate  
Phase 4.7 → Detect & Steer  
Phase 4.6 → Human Language  
Phase 5 → Ethical Close  

No overlaps. No conflicts.

---

## KEY PRINCIPLE (TO AVOID FUTURE CONFUSION)
If content is:
- proactive → Phase 6
- reactive → Phase 7
- behavioral → Runtime
- persuasive close → Phase 5

